latestIgtvVideos.title: *FINALLYYY* My Hairstyling Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
* This is not a sponsored video * 

It’s been months and months ever since y’all have been asking how I style my hair and finally it’s here! 🤍

I use the @dyson_india Airwrap ( Volume & Shape Kit ) in 2 simple steps and finish it off with my @lorealindia 
Mythic Oil! 

Personally, I feel the @dyson_india Airwrap is an investment! The change I see in my hair after using it for 2 whole years is absolutely insane, they’re always soft and shiny because there’s minimal heat damage!

Incase you don’t have the machine, follow the same technique with any heat brush and curling iron following the direction of
wrapping your hair around the rod! 

Happy Styling Girls ♥️♥️ if you recreate the style, use the hashtag #stylewithmt
